<h3 data-start="1065" data-end="1123">Les différences culturelles affectent-elles la vie universitaire ?</h3>
<p data-start="1124" data-end="1290">Très peu. Les universités sont généralement des environnements internationaux. Les cours en anglais, les bureaux des étudiants étrangers et les services de conseil offrent un grand soutien pour l&#8217;adaptation culturelle.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-05-29T08:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-14T15:49:50Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/international-students-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Social life for international students studying at universities in Turkey.","title":"international-students-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'fr' AND "slug" = 'les-stereotypes-culturels-en-turquie-comment-les-comprendre-et-les-depasser' );
